{"type": "article", "id": 10438, "title": "Poise Design x Superga 婚纱运动鞋", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-05T07:14:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235632IjYTtJMGoE547yHh.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">今年运动鞋在时尚圈的有多火？总之现在连结婚都有人选择穿运动鞋了。最近，黎巴嫩女鞋品牌Poise Design 和意大利帆布鞋品牌 Superga 联合推出了一个婚鞋系列。这个系列鞋子采用 Superga 经典白色鞋款为原型，加入施华洛世奇水晶，珍珠和蝴蝶结等浪漫的婚礼元素。其中有一款还印有 “I Do” 字样，浪漫又时尚满满。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235630v1LhzJpAoesEjGFm.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235631Hb6uXvpTonsDxt01.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235631ITQSrB2xOKgLEkad.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<br>\n\n\n"}